PCI-compliant systems ensure data security and reliability.', metrics: ['24/7 coverage capability', 'Cloud-based telephony', 'Enterprise security'] }, { title: 'Industry Partnerships', icon: Shield, description: 'Established relationships with major providers and master dealers including Allconnect, Ibex, P10, and RSI.', metrics: ['Texas Electricity contract', 'Multiple ISP integrations', 'Energy sector expertise'] }, { title: 'AI-Powered Operations', icon: Zap, description: 'Advanced technology stack including automated order reconciliation, AI quality assurance, and real-time analytics.', metrics: ['Order Recon system', 'AI-driven QA', 'Performance tracking'] } ]; const coreServices = [ { service: 'Internet Services', providers: 'AT&T, Viasat, Metronet, Rise Broadband, HughesNet', volume: '1,000-2,000 calls/month' }, { service: 'Energy Services', providers: 'Texas Electricity Ratings partnership', volume: '4 full-time dedicated agents' }, { service: 'Home Services', providers: 'Security, TV, phone bundles', volume: 'Multi-vertical capability' } ]; return (
